n. Monolayer WTe2\ntherefore presents an exceptional combination of topological properties and\nstrong correlations over a wide temperature range.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Oct 2021 00:50:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-09"}
