 but one needs to run it on a quantum computer to\nproduce a string with the guaranteed performance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Oct 2021 06:35:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Jan 2022 18:50:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 7 Jul 2022 13:35:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-08"}
