ius, and as L1489 IRS is close to the end of mass accretion phase, our\nresult suggests that only a fraction of a dense core eventually forms a star.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Oct 2021 06:51:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-02"}
