ates of the total\nkinetic energy or the component parallel to the LOS. This is due to some plasma\noutside the formation temperature range of the ion, the multi-directional\ndriver, and cancellation of the velocity along the LOS. The impact each factor\nhas on the estimation is dependent on the set up of the model and the chosen\nemission line.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Oct 2021 08:16:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-11"}
