 via vaccination mandates and advertisement\ncampaigns is unnecessary for the older population, for the younger population\n(ages: 20-39), some encouragement from the government via media campaigns and\nvaccine mandates may be necessary.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Oct 2021 09:17:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Feb 2023 01:14:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-24"}
