rs. Previously known, essentially optimal, regularity results are\nincluded as special cases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Oct 2021 11:04:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Jun 2022 08:17:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-01"}
