or \\ecp and \\bocp. \\end{itemize}\nFinally we present an $\\mathcal{O}^*(2^{|V(G)|})$ algorithm for the \\bcp,\ngeneralizing the known algorithm with a similar bound for the standard\nchromatic number.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Oct 2021 15:12:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-28"}
